freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Left hip, back and left leg pain was evident for the last four days. It was difficult to stand and walk for extended periods. It seems less pronounced today, however.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I had a headache last night followed by my first ever nosebleed at 11:00. I wasn't sure if the vaccine had anything to do with it, but wanted to report it. I was tired  today due to less sleep.
